{"tid":1103834,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一首分手後聽用黎療傷既歌","createTime":"2019-04-12T16:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T10:29:28.000Z","uid":121040,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b78bbbfac54e629d8207c9a2c7b8191350123f9c","tid":1103834,"uid":121040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"愛情來的時候，一首首情歌都突然有了意義，有了畫面。<br />\n<br />\n同樣，當愛情死去的時候，一首首傷心情歌的一字一句也突然變得像錐心之痛，讓你痛的不是歌詞，而是歌詞背後你想起跟她/他的一個個畫面，但是，生活，人生，時間不會為你停下，始終我地需要放下，傷口最後也結成不痛不癢的疤痕，而我地都需要歌曲用作療傷既藥<br />\n<br />\n大家不如一齊分享下一首你分手後聽到會令你釋懷既歌。<br />\n<br />\n我先：不來也不去 - 陳奕迅"},{"pid":"f654e1f48d0b2573d799186986db1855de802bca","tid":1103834,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:17:04.000Z","msg":"傷心的人別聽慢歌"},{"pid":"1c07cc4839274055a8a58c444e52b88175561fcf","tid":1103834,"uid":121040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:17:30.000Z","msg":"btw,內容係十三道佬味巴打作既<br />\n我只係加少少野上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5749c4976ebdc2bbe37ed08224a7ed45c8049226","tid":1103834,"uid":121040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:25:11.000Z","msg":"No rain no rainbow - babymetal"},{"pid":"f7243543d516d8bcd5f1b83fe87a31cae4f4a120","tid":1103834,"uid":140590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T17:41:56.000Z","msg":"生命樹<br />\n失戀的意義<br />\n理智與感情"},{"pid":"32036833ea9300273adb1fbd59cf289c166724f1","tid":1103834,"uid":199265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T17:42:54.000Z","msg":"藉口"},{"pid":"60adbf19975fac550a5f2b7657042086087bc0d8","tid":1103834,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T17:48:16.000Z","msg":"失戀咁down緊係要聽啲輕快啲嘅，呢首淨係個solo都可以用嚟打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMegadeth - Tornado of Souls"},{"pid":"e0dca6735acf2f0e08b15ca1c3959ead3752ff24","tid":1103834,"uid":247958,"like":